field.value:
On Castle.ActiveRecord/Framework/Internal/Visitors/XmlGenerationVisitor.cs: 208 (line 256 in beta3, I believe), conversion to lowercase does not use InvariantCulture. On Turkish locale, lowercase of I is ? (dotless i, if your browser can't display that), not i. NHibernate fails to parse resulting hbm with the following message:

{"could not instantiate id generator for strategy '?dentity'"}

Resolution:

line should read:
className = model.PrimaryKeyAtt.Generator.ToString().ToLower(CultureInfo.InvariantCulture);

There are 6 ToLower statements total in XmlGenerationVisitor.
